Merritt Butrick https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Merritt_Butrick 0 Merritt R. Butrick (September 3, 1959 – March 17, 1989) was an American actor, known for his roles on the teen sitcom Square Pegs (1982), in two Star Trek feature films, and a variety of other acting roles in the 1980s.
